  "description": "The second billiards game in the <i>Simple 1500 Series</i>. The game supports player vs player or player vs AI matches. There are seven AI opponents, three of which can be unlocked by beating the starting four. There are couple of difference ambients and tables to choose from before each match. The gameplay uses fixed camera behind the stick with ability to rotate in the direction of the shot, change the point where the cue hits the ball and vertical angle. At the beginning of each match who starts first is determined by banking (each player hits the ball, and whichever ball bounces closer back to the player, wins).",
